forbidden.name: fsd-shared-isolation

forbidden.name: fsd-entities-layer

forbidden.name: fsd-no-cross-slice-features
forbidden.comment: Feature slices should not import from other feature slices directly.

forbidden.name: fsd-ui-isolation

forbidden.name: fsd-public-api
